narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend Yoruba to anyone that needs to fulfill their language requirement. It is a lot of fun to learn about a culture that you likely hadn't heard about before coming to Yale.

L3 Yoruba is a continuation of the first year of Yoruba. The topics are slightly harder, but the class is just as fun and rewarding as ever. Continue with the language - you won't regret it! It has definitely been my favorite class at Yale.
